<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>電子郵件驗證 - 忘記密碼</title>
    <style>
        .validation-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .alert {
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .alert-danger {
            color: #721c24;
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border-color: #f5c6cb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="validation-container">
        <h2>電子郵件驗證</h2>

        @if (!ViewData.ModelState.IsValid)
        {
            <div class="alert alert-danger">
                @Html.ValidationSummary(false, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
            </div>
        }

        <p>系統正在驗證您的電子郵件...</p>
        <p>如果沒有自動跳轉，請點擊下方按鈕</p>

        @Html.ActionLink("返回登入頁面", "Login", "Members", null, new { @class = "btn btn-primary" })
    </div>
</body>
</html>